'''''Inspector Gadget and the Circus of Fear''''' is a [[video game]] based on the [[Inspector Gadget (1983 TV series)|television show of the same name]].

==Plot==
When the International Circus comes to town, a mysterious series of disappearances begin, and [[Inspector Gadget (character)|Inspector Gadget]] is called into help. Once his involvement is discovered, [[Penny (Inspector Gadget)|Penny]] and [[Brain (Inspector Gadget)|Brain]] are kidnapped, making Gadget's task bigger. He must get through each side-scrolling level, avoiding the meanies by jumping on them to reach the final target. There are many holes which lead to different sections of levels. The [[Commodore 64|C64]] version adds an icon system allowing players to collect and use their gadgets.

